  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated by vibrant fireworks. A long, illuminated bridge stretches across dark water, leading towards a densely packed urban landscape. The city is a tapestry of twinkling lights, forming a dynamic and captivating silhouette. Above the city, colorful fireworks explode in bursts of red, green, and gold, adding to the dramatic and celebratory atmosphere. The foreground consists of dark water reflecting a few sparse lights, creating a sense of depth. The scene evokes a feeling of wonder and excitement.",
